title: Avey Tare's Slasher Flicks - Enter the Slasher House
description:
Avey Tare's Slasher Flicks is a new band featuring Animal Collective member Avey Tare, ex-Dirty Projectors member Angel Deradoorian and ex-Ponytail drummer Jeremy Hyman. The trio have announced their debut LP Enter the Slasher House, out April 8 in the U.S. and April 7 internationally via Domino. 

Found this leaked version online, and I thought I'd share. Track 8 is missing, I know,...but I don't know why - haven't been able to find it anywhere.
